Package: polio.wpv1.phylodynamics
Title: WPV1 Phylogeographic Analysis Template
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Syed Adnan", "Haider", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Reproducible R scripts for exploratory WPV1 phylogeographic analysis using dated trees, stochastic character mapping, movement summaries, and lineage summaries. The public repository includes synthetic example data only.
